    <p>I’m a Montreal-based designer specializing in interrelating people and technology through reductive design and code.</p>
    <p>Currently shaping the future of open photography as the Head of Design at <a href="https://unsplash.com" target="_blank">Unsplash</a>.</p>
    <p>Outside of my day-to-day, I enjoy traveling and taking <a href="https://instagram.com/kirillz" target="_blank">photos</a> with my pocket camera-phone.</p>
    <p>Find me elsewhere on the web: <a href="https://twitter.com/kirillz" target="_blank">Twitter</a>, <a href="https://dribbble.com/kirillz" target="_blank">Dribbble</a>, <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/kirillzakharov" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a> or e-mail me at &#x2937;&#xFE0E; <a href="mailto:i%6e%66%6f@%6b&#105;ri%6c%6cz.%63&#111;%6d">info@kirillz.com</a>.</p>
