    <h3>Projects</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <p>
          <a href="https://awards.unsplash.com" target="_blank">Unsplash Awards</a> <sup>&#x2197;&#xFE0E; Project</sup>
          <br>
          A yearly celebration created to recognize the powerful impact Unsplash contributors have made through their generosity and artistry.
          <br>
          <small>In collaboration with Charles Deluvio, Unsplash</small>
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>
          <a href="https://unsplash.com/developers" target="_blank">Unsplash for Developers</a> <sup>&#x2197;&#xFE0E; Project</sup>
          <br>
          The Unsplash API is used in over 6,000 third-party applications, including Medium, Trello, Adobe, Google, Typeform, Codepen, InVision and Product Hunt.
          <br>
          <small>In collaboration with Charles Deluvio, Unsplash</small>
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>
          <a href="https://unsplash.com/apps/ios" target="_blank">Unsplash for iOS</a> <sup>&#x2197;&#xFE0E; App</sup>
          <br>
          Official Unsplash app for iOS.
          <br>
          <small>In collaboration with Olivier Collet, Charles Deluvio, Unsplash</small>
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>
          <a href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/unsplash-instant/pejkokffkapolfffcgbmdmhdelanoaih" target="_blank">Unsplash Instant</a> <sup>&#x2197;&#xFE0E; Extension</sup>
          <br>
          A Google Chrome extension that shows a random photo from Unsplash every time you open a new tab.
          <br>
          <small>In collaboration with Luke Chesser, Charles Lalonde</small>
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>
          <a href="https://medium.com/unsplash/unsplash-figma-cf03195e9f9a" target="_blank">Unsplash for Figma</a> <sup>&#x2197;&#xFE0E; Plugin</sup>
          <br>
          Official Unsplash plugin for Figma.
          <br>
          <small>In collaboration with Liam Martens</small>
        </p>
      </li>
